nd \"Imitation of Life.\" with\nClaudette Colbert.\nthe screen, \"Pent\nPARK\nhow PLAYING\u2014\"In old Chicago,' ith\nOn C Mv a Kn\u00ab n 'SS'buSZS' sunwyrk'T.Jd\nJoel McCrae Selected shorts and news\nFRIDAY -SATDRDAY\u2014 \"Pearl ol Death.\"\nwith Basil Rathbone and Nigel Bruce Also\n\u25a0\u25a0Raiders of Red Gap,\" with Bob Livingston\nand A1 St. John. Chapter three ol \"Valley\nand selected shorts and\nof Vanishing\n^SUNDAY MONDAY \"Objective.\nOn the\nBurma,\"\nprogram.\nwith Jim Wakeley\nSelected program of\nwith Errol Flynn.\n\"Springtime in Texas.\"\nand Dennis Moore.\nTUESDAA'TwKDNLSDAY- -\"Good Luck. Mr\nYates.\" with Claire Trevor. On the same\nprogram, \"Murder, My Sweet. with Dick\nP TOtJRSDAY. t SATtiRDAY\u2014\"Babes on Swing\n*lir t, 'oowbM P n\"the Otoadt\" with\"Charles\nStkrrett. chapter tour ol \"Valley of Vanish\nta co\u00eeflNG-\"Bowei C to'Broadway\"'with'Don\naid O'Connor, and Peggy Ryan.\nRIALTO\nnow showing\u2014R obert Young and Dorothy\nMcGuire in \"The Enchanted Cottage.\" On\nprogram \"Fashion Model\" with Rob\nAlso the\non the same pro\n1 now showing\u2014W allace Beery and James\nOleason in \"This Man's Navy.\" Also on the\nsame program, \"Blonde Fever,\" with Phillip\nI Dorn and Mary Astor.\nSTARTS SUNDAY\u2014Roy Rogers in \"The Man\nProm Oklahoma.\" On the same program.!\nthe\nert Lowery and Marjorie Weaver.\nlatest Fox Movietone News.\nSTARTS SUNDAY\u2014Fred MacMurray in\n\u2022Captain Eddie,\" with Lynn Bari. On the\nsame program, \"Two \u00a9Clock Courage.\" with\nTom Conway and Ann Rutherford. Plus the\nlatest Fox News events.\nSTARTS THURSDAY\u2014\"The Picture of\nDorian Grey,\" with Hurd Hatfield, George\nSanders and Donna Reed,\ngram. \"Tell It to a Star,\" with Robert Liv\ningstone and Ruth Terry.\nPox Movietone News.\nCOMING\u2014\"Back to Bataan 1\nWayne and Phllit Ahn.\nAMERICAN\nAIso the latest\nwith John\n\"Trouble Chasers\" with Maxie Rosenbloom\nI and Billie Gilbert.\nI THEATRE CLOSED WEDNESDAY.\nSTARTS THURSDAY